Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.39,0:01:00.44,OP_EN,,0,0,0,,{\be1}The Rock City Boy
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.84,0:01:04.64,OP,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Oh baby 跳吧 跳吧 跳越牆壁 With my guitar
