Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.29,0:01:10.00,OP,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Just music 僅僅只是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.00,0:01:12.78,OP,,0,0,0,,{\be1}奉獻給你喔 oh yeah
