Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.29,0:01:47.87,OP_EN,,0,0,0,,{\be1}I wanna believe the singing on beat
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.87,0:01:49.56,OP_EN,,0,0,0,,{\be1}most recently is like recess for me
